item.title: COVID-19 Outbreaks in Healthcare Institutions
item.description: Author: Ruihan Zhang Abstraction During COVID-19,healthcare institutions are the first line of the outbreaks, my goal is to find the most regular continued time for COVID_19 outbreaks. In addition, I want to find the type of healthcare institutions that outbreaks most possible to happen. I use Wickham et al. (2019), Gelfand (2020)ï¼Œ Wickham et al. (2020). Introduction This dataset is about the outbreaks in Toronto healthcare institutions (including hospitals, long-term care homes and retirement homes).
